               <p>I <rs id="t17820410-40-viclabel218" type="occupation">keep a brokers shop</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17820410-40-victim524 t17820410-40-viclabel218"></join>, the front is open, I saw the prisoner reach his hand, and take the candlesticks off a table, he did not come in, I saw him take them, I pursued him, and took them from him, he said he found them.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I left off work, and was a little in liquor, and coming from the o-other side of the water, I fell right against the shop, and knocked the candlesticks down, I took them up, I acknowledge having them in my hand, I am ready to go to sea.</p>
